ComicInfo.Summary: It's been 15 years since the death of Mistress Nyx, and the world is slowly recovering - but this isn't a world we've ever seen before. This is a world where the natural and the supernatural have merged to create a dangerous new place - a world very much in need of Vampirella. In this issue, the Drujh weapons have hatched and are about to be unleashed upon Sepulcher City. It's up to Vampirella and the agents of the Danse Macabre to stop the demonic weaponry any way they possibly can. But will a journey to Hell itself to find the answer be enough in the thrilling conclusion of the Hell weaponry storyline? Enter the world of Vampirella Strikes under a series of amazing covers by returning superstars Lucio Parillo, Stephen Segovia, Jung-Geun Yoon, and another stunning cosplay cover featuring Rachel Hollon as Vampirella!
